---
title: Tropical Pulled Chicken Bowl on Green Onion Rice with Mango-Poblano Salsa
description: Get a taste of the tropics with this bright and fresh chicken bowl! Tender BBQ chicken, juicy mango and peppery poblano strike the perfect balance between sweet and savoury that will have you reaching for seconds.
